addBallot(string,string,bool,string).details: Adds a ballot to the election

params._ipfsCid: IPFS CID for detailed ballot data

addElectionMetadata(string,string).details: Adds IPFS metadata to the election

addVoter(address,string,uint256,bytes32).details: Adds a single voter to the election

params._voterKeyHash: Hash of the voter's key for authentication

addVoters(address[],string[],uint256[],s.details: Adds multiple voters to the election in a batch

params._ipfsCid: IPFS CID for detailed voter data
params._voterIds: Array of unique IDs for voters

castVote(string,bytes32[],string).details: Casts a vote with wallet authentication

params._choices: Array of candidate choices (as bytes32 hashes)

castVoteWithKey(string,bytes32,bytes32[].details: Casts a vote with key authentication (without wallet)

params._choices: Array of candidate choices (as bytes32 hashes)

castVoteWithPaymaster(string,bytes32,byt.details: Casts a vote through a paymaster (gasless voting)

params._choices: Array of candidate choices (as bytes32 hashes)

deleteElection().details: Deletes an election (soft delete by changing status)

getVote(string).details: Gets the vote cast by a voter

getVoter(string).details: Gets voter information by voter ID

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

registerVoterKey(bytes32).details: Registers a voter key for authentication

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

verifyVoterAccess(string,bytes32).details: Verifies if a voter has access to vote
